      "name": "Class III VAD centrifugal pump applicability domain",
      "description": "Model applies to centrifugal blood pumps operating as Class III VADs with impeller tip speeds between 2000 and 6000 RPM, blood viscosity 0.0035–0.004 Pa·s (hematocrit 35–45%), and inlet flow rates 3–8 L/min. Hemolysis predictions are valid only within this parametric envelope and are not extrapolated to axial-flow or pulsatile-assist geometries."
    },
