      "rationale": "Iterative convergence was monitored to residual levels below 10⁻⁶ for all equations. Mass imbalance across the domain was < 0.01%. Time-averaged quantities showed < 0.5% variation over the last 5 impeller revolutions. Floating-point precision effects were assessed by comparison of double- and single-precision runs; differences < 0.1% in NIH.",
